                SIMBA HELP PAGE
WELCOME TO THE SIMBA HELP PAGE
------------------------------
Simba is a Mini Banking System cofounded by Mandre, Haggai, Marina, Alpha and Gilbert.
We offer no profits and charge minimal interest.
To get started, sign up with us. You can then Send Money, Withdraw money and deposit 
Money. 

HOW TO DEPOSIT AND WITHDRAW MONEY
    To deposit and withdraw money, you must visit Simba Mini Bank agent. The agent generates 
for you a transaction token. Each transaction token is tied to a financial figure. You then enter
the amount you want to withdraw or deposit along with the transation toke. If the values match, your 
transaction proceeds. But if it fails, the transaction is declined.
    
You can get more assistance by using our website.
